---
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Example Products API (example based)
  version: 1.0.0
  contact: {}
servers:
  - url: "{{host}}"
paths:
  "/product/{id}":
    get:
      summary: "GET /products/:id"
      description: Get single product
      operationId: "get/products/:id"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "GET /products/:id"
          headers:
            Access-Control-Allow-Origin:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "*"
            Connection:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: keep-alive
            Content-Length:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "79"
            Date:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "Tue, 04 May 2021 10:22:58 GMT"
            ETag:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "W/\"4f-aj8zSH7MB6cvQn56hAlIKZ+G1BE\""
            X-Powered-By:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: Express
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  id:
                    type: string
                    example: "09"
                  name:
                    type: string
                    example: Gem Visa
                  price:
                    type: number
                    example: 99.99
                  type:
                    type: string
                    example: CREDIT_CARD
                  version:
                    type: string
                    example: v1
              examples:
                "GET /products/:id":
                  value:
                    id: "09"
                    name: Gem Visa
                    price: 99.99
                    type: CREDIT_CARD
                    version: v1
        "404":
          description: "GET /products/:id (404)"
          headers:
            Access-Control-Allow-Origin:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "*"
            Connection:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: keep-alive
            Content-Length:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "79"
            Date:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "Tue, 04 May 2021 10:22:58 GMT"
            ETag:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "W/\"4f-aj8zSH7MB6cvQn56hAlIKZ+G1BE\""
            X-Powered-By:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: Express
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties: {}
              examples:
                "GET /products/:id (404)":
                  value: {}
    parameters:
      - name: id
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
  /products:
    get:
      summary: GET /products
      description: Get all products
      operationId: get/products
      responses:
        "200":
          description: GET /products
          headers:
            Access-Control-Allow-Origin:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "*"
            Connection:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: keep-alive
            Content-Length:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "246"
            Date:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "Tue, 04 May 2021 10:30:59 GMT"
            ETag:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "W/\"f6-H4sUa2b5P0f86z9trNUSS1xGqeo\""
            X-Powered-By:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: Express
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    id:
                      type: string
                      example: "09"
                    name:
                      type: string
                      example: Gem Visa
                    price:
                      type: number
                      example: 99.99
                    type:
                      type: string
                      example: CREDIT_CARD
                    version:
                      type: string
                      example: v1
              examples:
                GET /products:
                  value:
                    - id: "09"
                      name: Gem Visa
                      price: 99.99
                      type: CREDIT_CARD
                      version: v1
                    - id: "10"
                      name: 28 Degrees
                      price: 49.49
                      type: CREDIT_CARD
                      version: v1
                    - id: "11"
                      name: MyFlexiPay
                      price: 16.5
                      type: PERSONAL_LOAN
                      version: v2
    post:
      summary: POST /products/ (200)
      description: Create a product
      operationId: post/products/(200)
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                id:
                  type: string
                  example: "09"
                name:
                  type: string
                  example: Gem Visa
                price:
                  type: number
                  example: 99.99
                type:
                  type: string
                  example: CREDIT_CARD
                version:
                  type: string
                  example: v1
            example:
              id: "09"
              name: Gem Visa
              price: 99.99
              type: CREDIT_CARD
              version: v1
      responses:
        "200":
          description: POST /products/ (200)
          headers:
            Access-Control-Allow-Origin:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "*"
            Connection:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: keep-alive
            Content-Length:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "79"
            Date:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "Sun, 09 May 2021 12:29:53 GMT"
            ETag:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "W/\"4f-7upA8VUHobjcwMU2JZU+mGYVfEo\""
            X-Powered-By:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: Express
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  id:
                    type: string
                    example: "09"
                  name:
                    type: string
                    example: Gem Visa
                  price:
                    type: number
                    example: 99.99
                  type:
                    type: string
                    example: CREDIT_CARD
                  version:
                    type: string
                    example: v1
              examples:
                POST /products/ (200):
                  value:
                    id: "09"
                    name: Gem Visa
                    price: 99.99
                    type: CREDIT_CARD
                    version: v1
        "400":
          description: POST /products/ (400)
          headers:
            Access-Control-Allow-Origin:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "*"
            Connection:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: keep-alive
            Content-Length:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "29"
            Date:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "Sun, 09 May 2021 13:07:38 GMT"
            ETag:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: "W/\"1d-pnhbRSD4NZML3cnaJuyottC+RiE\""
            X-Powered-By:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: Express
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: invalid product
              examples:
                POST /products/ (400):
                  value:
                    message: invalid product
tags: []
